'''Code of Crimmor''' described the various rules and laws that determined which activities were permitted or forbidden in the [[Amn]]ian city of [[Crimmor]].{{Cite dragon/334/Crimmor: City of Caravans|22-34}}

{{quote|''Crimmor's laws are whatever the mayor says they are, and he speaks differently when the accused is wealthy than he does when a prisoner has few coins.''|
Crimman rumor}}
